[[!meta title="Partners"]]

Welcome, we're glad to see you interested in becoming a partner!
It's because of our partners' substantial support that we are able to maintain
and improve Tails.

Become a partner
================

To be listed as a partner on our [[partner page|partners]], at least one of the
criteria below must be met. A partner provides either:

* A unique substantial financial donation to Tails
* Ongoing substantial financial support to Tails such as a yearly donation
* A grant or funding to Tails
* Hardware, equipment, travel sponsorships etc. (in-kind donation)

You'll be listed on our sponsors page under the year for which receive your donation.

For detailed information please get in touch with us at <mailto:tails-fundraising@boum.org>.
